    FROM [ProductCategories] AS [x0]

""SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [x].[CategoryId], [x].[Content], [x].[DateCreated], [x].[DateModified], [x].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([x].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [x].[Id], [x].[Image], [x].[Name], [x].[OriginalPrice], [x].[Price], CASE

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, CASE
    WHEN [x].[CategoryId] IS NULL
    THEN NULL ELSE [x.ProductCategory].[DateCreated]
END AS [DateCreated0], [x.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [x.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [x.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [x.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [x.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [x.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [x.ProductCategory].[Status], [x].[PromotionPrice], [x].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [x].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [x].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [x].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [x].[Status] AS [Status0], [x].[Tags], [x].[Unit], [x].[ViewCount], [x.ProductCategory].[Id]

    WHEN [x.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Address], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Avatar], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[BirthDay], CASE
    WHEN [x.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN NULL ELSE CASE
        WHEN [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId] IS NULL
        THEN NULL ELSE [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[DateCreated]
    END
END AS [DateCreated], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[DateModified], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Email], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[FullName], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Gender], CASE
    WHEN [x.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN NULL ELSE CASE
        WHEN [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId] IS NULL
        THEN NULL ELSE [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Id]
    END
END AS [Id0], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[PhoneNumber], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Status], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[UserName], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[BillStatus], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerAddress], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerMessage], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerMobile], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerName], CASE
    WHEN [x.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN NULL ELSE [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[DateCreated]
END AS [DateCreated0], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [x.BillDetails].[BillId], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[PaymentMethod], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[Status] AS [Status0], CASE
    WHEN [x.BillDetails].[ColorId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [dtoBillDetail.Color].[Code], [x.BillDetails].[ColorId], [dtoBillDetail.Color].[Name], [x.BillDetails].[Id] AS [Id1], [x.BillDetails].[Price], [x.BillDetails].[ProductId], [x.BillDetails].[Quantity], CASE
    WHEN [x.BillDetails].[SizeId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.BillDetails].[SizeId], [dtoBillDetail.Size].[Name] AS [Name0], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Id]
FROM [BillDetails] AS [x.BillDetails]
INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [dtoBillDetail.Size] ON [x.BillDetails].[SizeId] = [dtoBillDetail.Size].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [dtoBillDetail.Color] ON [x.BillDetails].[ColorId] = [dtoBillDetail.Color].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [dtoBillDetail.Bill] ON [x.BillDetails].[BillId] = [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AppUsers] AS [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser] ON [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId] = [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [x0].[PromotionPrice], [x0].[Id]
    FROM [Products] AS [x0]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
    WHERE ([x0].[Status] = 1) AND [x0].[PromotionPrice] IS NOT NULL
    ORDER BY [x0].[PromotionPrice] DESC, [x0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [x.BillDetails].[ProductId] = [t].[Id]

END AS [DateCreated0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Id] AS [Id2], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Status], [dtoProductTag.Product].[PromotionPrice], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Status] AS [Status0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Tags], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Unit], [dtoProductTag.Product].[ViewCount], [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[TagId], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Id]
FROM [ProductTags] AS [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [dtoProductTag.Product] ON [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [dtoProductTag.Product].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory] ON [dtoProductTag.Product].[CategoryId] = [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t0].[DateCreated], [t0].[Id], [x.BlogTags0].[Id] AS [Id0], [dtoBlogTag.Tag0].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [BlogTags] AS [x.BlogTags0]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [dtoBlogTag.Tag0] ON [x.BlogTags0].[TagId] = [dtoBlogTag.Tag0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [x1].[DateCreated], [x1].[Id]
        FROM [Blogs] AS [x1]
        WHERE [x1].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x1].[DateCreated] DESC, [x1].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [x.BlogTags0].[BlogId] = [t0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[TagId] = [t1].[Id1]
ORDER BY [t1].[DateCreated] DESC, [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1], [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[Id], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Id], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x].[DateCreated], [x].[DateModified], [x].[Description], [x].[Id], [x].[Image], [x].[Name], [x].[ParentId], [x].[SeoAlias], [x].[SeoDescription], [x].[SeoKeywords], [x].[SeoPageTitle], [x].[SortOrder], [x].[Status]

2018-12-12T10:33:35.7767252+07:00 0HLIVSAC8P0EA:00000001 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("1"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [t].[SortOrder], [t].[Id], [x.Products].[CategoryId], [x.Products].[Content], [x.Products].[DateCreated], [x.Products].[DateModified], [x.Products].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [x.Products].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.Products].[Image], [x.Products].[Name], [x.Products].[OriginalPrice], [x.Products].[Price], [x.Products].[PromotionPrice], [x.Products].[SeoAlias], [x.Products].[SeoDescription], [x.Products].[SeoKeywords], [x.Products].[SeoPageTitle], [x.Products].[Status], [x.Products].[Tags], [x.Products].[Unit], [x.Products].[ViewCount]
FROM [Products] AS [x.Products]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x0].[SortOrder], [x0].[Id]
    FROM [ProductCategories] AS [x0]
    WHERE [x0].[ParentId] IS NULL

2018-12-12T10:33:37.8978466+07:00 0HLIVSAC8P0EA:00000001 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("1"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [t].[ParentId], [t].[SortOrder], [t].[Id], [x.Products].[CategoryId], [x.Products].[Content], [x.Products].[DateCreated], [x.Products].[DateModified], [x.Products].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [x.Products].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.Products].[Image], [x.Products].[Name], [x.Products].[OriginalPrice], [x.Products].[Price], [x.Products].[PromotionPrice], [x.Products].[SeoAlias], [x.Products].[SeoDescription], [x.Products].[SeoKeywords], [x.Products].[SeoPageTitle], [x.Products].[Status], [x.Products].[Tags], [x.Products].[Unit], [x.Products].[ViewCount]
FROM [Products] AS [x.Products]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x0].[ParentId], [x0].[SortOrder], [x0].[Id]

    SELECT [x0].[SortOrder], [x0].[Id]
    FROM [ProductCategories] AS [x0]
    WHERE [x0].[ParentId] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [x.Products].[CategoryId] = [t].[Id]

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)

    WHEN [x].[CategoryId] IS NULL

END AS [DateCreated0], [x.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [x.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [x.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [x.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [x.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [x.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [x.ProductCategory].[Status], [x].[PromotionPrice], [x].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [x].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [x].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [x].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [x].[Status] AS [Status0], [x].[Tags], [x].[Unit], [x].[ViewCount], [x.ProductCategory].[Id]

    WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1

""SELECT [t].[ParentId], [t].[SortOrder], [t].[Id], [x.Products].[CategoryId], [x.Products].[Content], [x.Products].[DateCreated], [x.Products].[DateModified], [x.Products].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [x.Products].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.Products].[Image], [x.Products].[Name], [x.Products].[OriginalPrice], [x.Products].[Price], [x.Products].[PromotionPrice], [x.Products].[SeoAlias], [x.Products].[SeoDescription], [x.Products].[SeoKeywords], [x.Products].[SeoPageTitle], [x.Products].[Status], [x.Products].[Tags], [x.Products].[Unit], [x.Products].[ViewCount]
FROM [Products] AS [x.Products]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x0].[ParentId], [x0].[SortOrder], [x0].[Id]
    FROM [ProductCategories] AS [x0]
) AS [t] ON [x.Products].[CategoryId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[ParentId], [t].[SortOrder], [t].[Id], [x.Products].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
2018-12-12T12:38:03.3498460+07:00 0HLIVUFT23KTU:00000001 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("1"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [t1].[ParentId], [t1].[SortOrder], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], CASE
    WHEN [x.Products.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, CASE
    WHEN [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Address], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Avatar], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[BirthDay], CASE
    WHEN [x.Products.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN NULL ELSE CASE
        WHEN [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId] IS NULL
        THEN NULL ELSE [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[DateCreated]
    END
END AS [DateCreated], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[DateModified], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Email], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[FullName], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Gender], CASE
    WHEN [x.Products.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN NULL ELSE CASE
        WHEN [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId] IS NULL
        THEN NULL ELSE [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Id]
    END
END AS [Id1], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[PhoneNumber], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Status], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[UserName], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[BillStatus], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerAddress], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerId], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerMessage], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerMobile], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[CustomerName], CASE
    WHEN [x.Products.BillDetails].[BillId] IS NULL
    THEN NULL ELSE [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[DateCreated]
END AS [DateCreated0], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [x.Products.BillDetails].[BillId], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[PaymentMethod], [dtoBillDetail.Bill].[Status] AS [Status0], CASE
    WHEN [x.Products.BillDetails].[ColorId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [dtoBillDetail.Color].[Code], [x.Products.BillDetails].[ColorId], [dtoBillDetail.Color].[Name], [x.Products.BillDetails].[Id] AS [Id2], [x.Products.BillDetails].[Price], [x.Products.BillDetails].[ProductId], [x.Products.BillDetails].[Quantity], CASE
    WHEN [x.Products.BillDetails].[SizeId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.Products.BillDetails].[SizeId], [dtoBillDetail.Size].[Name] AS [Name0], [dtoBillDetail.Bill.AppUser].[Id]
FROM [BillDetails] AS [x.Products.BillDetails]
INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [dtoBillDetail.Size] ON [x.Products.BillDetails].[SizeId] = [dtoBillDetail.Size].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [dtoBillDetail.Color] ON [x.Products.BillDetails].[ColorId] = [dtoBillDetail.Color].[Id]

END AS [DateCreated0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Id] AS [Id2], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Status], [dtoProductTag.Product].[PromotionPrice], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Status] AS [Status0], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Tags], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Unit], [dtoProductTag.Product].[ViewCount], [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[TagId], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Id]
FROM [ProductTags] AS [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [dtoProductTag.Product] ON [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [dtoProductTag.Product].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory] ON [dtoProductTag.Product].[CategoryId] = [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t0].[DateCreated], [t0].[Id], [x.BlogTags0].[Id] AS [Id0], [dtoBlogTag.Tag0].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [BlogTags] AS [x.BlogTags0]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [dtoBlogTag.Tag0] ON [x.BlogTags0].[TagId] = [dtoBlogTag.Tag0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [x1].[DateCreated], [x1].[Id]
        FROM [Blogs] AS [x1]
        WHERE [x1].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x1].[DateCreated] DESC, [x1].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [x.BlogTags0].[BlogId] = [t0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[TagId] = [t1].[Id1]
ORDER BY [t1].[DateCreated] DESC, [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1], [dtoBlogTag.Tag.ProductTags].[Id], [dtoProductTag.Product].[Id], [dtoProductTag.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

2018-12-12T12:53:32.0349637+07:00 0HLIVUOIJM7S0:00000001 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("9"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [t].[SortOrder], [t].[Id], [x.Products].[CategoryId], [x.Products].[Content], [x.Products].[DateCreated], [x.Products].[DateModified], [x.Products].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [x.Products].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.Products].[Image], [x.Products].[Name], [x.Products].[OriginalPrice], [x.Products].[Price], [x.Products].[PromotionPrice], [x.Products].[SeoAlias], [x.Products].[SeoDescription], [x.Products].[SeoKeywords], [x.Products].[SeoPageTitle], [x.Products].[Status], [x.Products].[Tags], [x.Products].[Unit], [x.Products].[ViewCount]
FROM [Products] AS [x.Products]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x0].[SortOrder], [x0].[Id]
    FROM [ProductCategories] AS [x0]

""SELECT [t].[ParentId], [t].[SortOrder], [t].[Id], [x.Products].[CategoryId], [x.Products].[Content], [x.Products].[DateCreated], [x.Products].[DateModified], [x.Products].[Description], CAST(COALESCE([x.Products].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [x.Products].[Id] AS [Id0], [x.Products].[Image], [x.Products].[Name], [x.Products].[OriginalPrice], [x.Products].[Price], [x.Products].[PromotionPrice], [x.Products].[SeoAlias], [x.Products].[SeoDescription], [x.Products].[SeoKeywords], [x.Products].[SeoPageTitle], [x.Products].[Status], [x.Products].[Tags], [x.Products].[Unit], [x.Products].[ViewCount]
FROM [Products] AS [x.Products]
INNER JOIN (

    FROM [Products] AS [x.Products4]

        SELECT [x5].[ParentId], [x5].[SortOrder], [x5].[Id]
        FROM [ProductCategories] AS [x5]
